---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import profileImage from '../assets/profile.png';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<BaseLayout title="Jacob Monck">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">

    <div class="mb-10 flex justify-center">
      <div
        class="
          h-36 w-36
          rounded-full
          overflow-hidden
          shadow-xl
          ring-1 ring-zinc-800
          bg-zinc-950
          [mask-image:radial-gradient(circle,black_60%,transparent_100%)]
        "
      >
        <Image
          src={profileImage}
          alt="Photo of Jacob Monck"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover grayscale transition duration-300 hover:grayscale-0"
          loading="eager"
          width={144}
          height={144}
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight">
      Building thoughtful
      <span
        class="bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 via-yellow-400 via-green-400 via-blue-500 to-purple-500 bg-[length:300%_300%] bg-clip-text text-transparent animate-[rainbow_6s_linear_infinite]"
      >
        software.
      </span>
    </h1>

    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
      I focus on backend systems, APIs, and tooling, with an emphasis on correctness, performance, and maintainability.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-12 text-left">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">What I work on</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-4">
        My expertise lies in building robust backend solutions that power seamless experiences.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-300 space-y-1">
        <li>Designing and implementing scalable APIs</li>
        <li>Data modeling and database architecture</li>
        <li>Developing developer-friendly tooling</li>
        <li>Optimizing system performance</li>
        <li>Ensuring maintainable and clean codebases</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 text-left">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-3">Selected work</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
        A preview of some projects where Iâ€™ve solved complex backend challenges.
      </p>
      <div class="space-y-6 text-zinc-300">
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-zinc-100">API Gateway Optimization</p>
          <p>Streamlined request routing to reduce latency and improve throughput for high-traffic services.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-zinc-100">Data Synchronization System</p>
          <p>Built a reliable system ensuring consistent data replication across distributed databases.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="font-bold text-zinc-100">Custom Developer Tooling</p>
          <p>Created internal tools to automate deployment workflows and enhance developer productivity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center gap-4">
      <a
        href="/projects"
        class="rounded-lg bg-indigo-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-indigo-400 transition"
      >
        View Projects
      </a>

      <a
        href="/about"
        class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-zinc-300 hover:border-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-400 transition"
      >
        About Me
      </a>
    </div>

  </section>
</BaseLayout>
